        "descriptor": "Half-Time, Big Guitars"
      },
      "raw": "Breakdown - Half-Time, Big Guitars",
      "text": "I can miss you\nand still not answer\nI can love you\nand leave the room\nI can pray that you find daylight\nwithout becoming your moon\nI can hold all the good parts\nand still bury the blade\nI can remember your soft voice\nwithout entering the cage\nI can cry for the old us\nwithout pulling you through\nanother night where the worst thing\nI say becomes true",
      "lines": 14,
      "startT": 199.04,
      "endT": 236.24,
      "bars": 13
    },
