        "descriptor": "Female Lead"
      },
      "raw": "Final Chorus Variation - Female Lead",
      "text": "I won’t be your fire\nI won’t be your knife\nI won’t be the dark thing\nthat helps you hate your life\nI’ll leave a little light on\nbut I’m walking out now\nI won’t be your reason\nto keep breaking down",
      "lines": 8,
